]\)</p> <p>no 5</p> <p>\([1,9],[2,8],[3,7],[4,6]\)</p> <p>你可以發現到從 1~5 慢慢的從左到右每個 pair 的總和都少了 1</p> <p>ref : https://blog.csdn.net/C20181220_xiang_m_y/article/details/102564783</p> code <pre><code>#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;
#define int long long
#define pii pair&lt;int, int&gt;
#define pb push_back
#define mk make_pair
#define F first
#define S second
